{"title":"【JOI2017春季合宿】Port Facility","time_limit":6000,"memory_limit":1024,"url":"http://uoj.ac/problem/356","statement":[{"title":"# 题目描述","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<p>小M有两个本质不同的栈。</p>\n<p>无聊的小M找来了$n$个玩具。之后小M把这$n$个玩具随机顺序加入某一个栈或把他们弹出。</p>\n<p>现在小M告诉你每个玩具的入栈和出栈时间，现在她想考考小S，有多少种方案，把每个玩具分配给两个栈之一，并且存在一种满足小M告诉你的入栈和出栈时间的入栈序列。</p>\n<p>可怜的小S当然不知道啦，所以他求助于你。</p>\n"},{"title":"# 输入格式","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<p>第一行一个整数$n$。</p>\n<p>接下来$n$行，每行两个整数$l_i,r_i$，表示第$i$个玩具的入栈和出栈时间。</p>\n"},{"title":"# 输出格式","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<p>一行一个整数，表示答案<strong>对$10^9+7$取模的值</strong>。</p>\n"},{"title":"# 样例一","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<h4>input</h4>\n<pre>4\n1 3\n2 5\n4 8\n6 7\n\n</pre>\n\n<h4>output</h4>\n<pre>4\n\n</pre>\n\n"},{"title":"# 样例二","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<h4>input</h4>\n<pre>3\n1 4\n2 5\n3 6\n\n</pre>\n\n<h4>output</h4>\n<pre>0\n\n</pre>\n\n\n"},{"title":"# 样例三","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<h4>input</h4>\n<pre>5\n1 4\n2 10\n6 9\n7 8\n3 5\n\n</pre>\n\n<h4>output</h4>\n<pre>8\n\n</pre>\n\n\n\n"},{"title":"# 样例四","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<h4>input</h4>\n<pre>8\n1 15\n2 5\n3 8\n4 6\n14 16\n7 9\n10 13\n11 12\n\n</pre>\n\n<h4>output</h4>\n<pre>16\n\n</pre>\n\n\n"},{"title":"# 限制与约定","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<p>对于所有数据，</p>\n<p>$1\\le n\\le 10^6,1\\le l_i &lt; r_i \\le 2n$，$l_i,r_i$互不相同。</p>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n <table class=\"table table-bordered table-text-center table-vertical-middle\"><thead><tr><th>子任务</th>\n    <th>分值</th>\n    <th>$n$</th>\n   </tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td>\n    <td>10</td>\n    <td>$\\le 20$</td>\n   </tr><tr><td>2</td>\n    <td>12</td>\n    <td>$\\le 2000$</td>\n   </tr><tr><td>3</td>\n    <td>56</td>\n    <td>$\\le 10^5$</td>\n   </tr><tr><td>4</td>\n    <td>22</td>\n    <td>$\\le 10^6$</td>\n   </tr></tbody></table></div>\n\n<p><strong>时间限制：</strong>$6\\texttt{s}$</p>\n<p><strong>空间限制：</strong>$1024\\texttt{MB}$</p>\n"},{"title":"# 下载","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<p><a href=\"/download.php?type=problem&amp;id=356\">样例数据下载</a></p>\n\n"}]}